column2: select   id, s.bestobjID as objid, s.specObjID as specobjid, s.z as zspec, s.zErr,   zWarning as zW, sciencePrimary as prim, s.plate, s.mjd, s.fiberid,    snMedian as SN, bptclass as bpt, lgm_tot_p5# as smass, sfr_tot_p5# as sfr,    specsfr_tot_p5# as ssfr, oh_p5# as oh, d4#_n as d4#n, lick_hb as hb,    lick_hd_a as hd, lick_hg_a as hg, h_delta_eqw as Hd_EW, h_gamma_eqw as Hg_EW,   h_beta_eqw as Hb_EW, h_alpha_eqw as Ha_EW, EW_Ha_#, Flux_OIII_#,    Flux_SII_#, Flux_SII_#, Flux_Ha_#, Flux_Hb_#   from MyDB.temp as t    left join SpecObjAll as s on s.bestObjID=t.objid    left join galSpecExtra as x on s.specObjID=x.specObjID   left join galSpecIndx as i on s.specObjID=i.specObjID   left join galSpecLine as l on s.specObjID=l.specObjID   left join emissionLinesPort as e on s.specObjID=e.specObjID   order by id
